{"type": "article", "id": 24448, "title": "圆筒竹家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134955v7GcEzCDkI8yJS52.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本创意机构 Stefan Diez Office 发起的竹家具系列项目，他们保留了竹子本来的样子。特别在于在桌椅等支柱结构上做了掏空处理，弯曲之后恰好可插入一根横向的竹子，以此来构成一种结构。竹家具是通过芳纶绳固定的，在三角形桌腿之间充当梁的结构。桌面用上了玻璃，而没有任何金属，尽量保持自然的竹筒效果。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021349535PEOfKd4TogGCjLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134954OPo9vybr5WJq6euF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40042373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134954AjETu7nigJ63tSHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134955Fx8zsRLVcBeNt3DK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40042373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}